.SYNOPSIS
    This PowerShell script ensures that Windows checks and reapplies registry-based GPO settings every time GPO refreshes 
    Author          : Hugh Black
    LinkedIn        : linkedin.com/in/hugh-black/
    GitHub          : github.com/hblack5676
    Date Created    : 2026-06-21
    Last Modified   : 2026-06-21
